301
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:05,630
Qiao Renyu!

302
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:07,680
Don't forget

303
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:10,410
you're still a prisoner
of the Imperial Army.

304
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:15,860
Can't you still understand

305
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:17,330
the current situation?

306
00:14:17,410 --> 00:14:19,810
With Specie Bank's backstop this morning,

307
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,790
the Chinese merchants
